{"tid":1928473,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］全台灣中學以下師生禁止出國","createTime":"2020-03-16T11:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T15:46:45.000Z","uid":323443,"like":39,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"02de722b09c6a795ba65da338ebf110db4549027","tid":1928473,"uid":323443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T11:49:35.000Z","msg":"行政院拍板！高中以下師生 本學期上課日期間禁止出國<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/120960/4418596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F120960%2F4418596&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=c8fcc9ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/120960/4418596</a><br />\n<br />\n對於多個地方政府宣布禁止高中以下師生出國，中央流行疫情指揮中心指揮官陳時中今（16）日宣布，行政院採納指揮中心的建議，認為此段時間再出國也不宜，因此決定高中以下的師生，到本學期上課日結束為止，將禁止出國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8CJZ6RFadR4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8CJZ6RFadR4&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=eb8bbe4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8CJZ6RFadR4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下重手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfdedbac3a34f8f06e4fd8ca682297d5fa9c97c9","tid":1928473,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T12:08:40.000Z","msg":"一刀切定有例外"},{"pid":"aa677fb5dc6eb08db78ce2daa465d2f41bf5ca2f","tid":1928473,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T12:13:20.000Z","msg":"太平時期：<br />\n蔡英文 &gt; 陳時中<br />\n<br />\n抗疫時期：<br />\n陳 &gt; 蔡"},{"pid":"ae67d94a27ddbdc2a86666e0421f23d2d674b4e5","tid":1928473,"uid":74368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T12:14:45.000Z","msg":"強勢政府"},{"pid":"bcc267f9c44d7ee22c95cbf1b2f1bf9612fdc462","tid":1928473,"uid":201374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa677fb5dc6eb08db78ce2daa465d2f41bf5ca2f","tid":1928473,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":1